==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Saami'''

# A nation of indigenous people living in [[Lapland]] of [[Finland]], [[Sweden]] and [[Norway]] and [[Kola Peninsula]] in [[Russia]]. Population: about 90,000.
# The [Finno-Ugric]] language of the Saami people.
# A person originating from the Saami nation.

